<!DOCTYPE subsection SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<subsection title="Print cards from the list view" id="printing" collapsed="true">
	<p>Click on the 'Print' link from the card list view.</p>
		<screenshot alttext="single card print" src="resources/images/print_link_from_list_view.png"/>
	<p>This will generate a .pdf file that contains all of cards from the current list view. Every page will contain two Mingle cards.</p>
	<p>Each printed card includes</p>
		<bullets>
			<item>card number</item>
			<item>card title</item>
			<item>card version information</item>
			<item>card description</item>
			<item>card properties</item>
			<item>tags</item>
		</bullets>
	<hint>Please note the card description will be <strong>truncated</strong>. Plus any charts in the card description and properties which have a value of (not set) will <strong>not</strong> be printed.</hint>
</subsection>
